        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/19895398/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/19895398/" class="">第163页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/evebeli/" class=" " title="Eve">Eve</a>
                (🍀)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="19895398">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">水深的河不会因投入一块石头便波涛汹涌，人也是如此。如果一个人受到欺侮便勃然大怒，那么他就不是大河，而是小水洼。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-07-24 23:47</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                水深的河不会因投入一块石头便波涛汹涌，人也是如此。如果一个人受到欺侮便勃然大怒，那么他就不是大河，而是小水洼。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
